575
00:27:16,090 --> 00:27:17,126
That sounds interesting.

576
00:27:17,770 --> 00:27:20,406
Our Limited Love Set today consists of,

577
00:27:20,430 --> 00:27:22,123
Cheating-Heart Minced Meat Salad,

578
00:27:23,900 --> 00:27:25,981
Shameless Seafood Salad,

579
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:28,486
Two-Timing Beef Steak,

580
00:27:28,510 --> 00:27:31,956
