581
00:27:31,981 --> 00:27:32,981
Interested?

582
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,969
It'll be served hot.

583
00:27:38,150 --> 00:27:39,323
Weird names, huh?

584
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:42,467
They're fusion dishes. Italian style

585
00:27:42,486 --> 00:27:44,460
with a touch of Northeastern Thai.

586
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:47,335
But don't worry. It won't be fishy.

587
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:49,575
We definitely serve fresh food here.

588
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:52,566
We don't tolerate anything fishy
or scandalous.

589
00:27:52,810 --> 00:27:53,810
Interested?

590
00:27:53,975 --> 00:27:54,975
Hmm…

591
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:58,344
Can I have some wine first?

592
00:27:58,730 --> 00:28:01,335
Allow me to shift the vibe a bit.

593
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:08,646
Now things are heating up,

594
00:28:08,664 --> 00:28:10,233
like you're rehearsing for hell.

595
00:28:10,763 --> 00:28:11,763
Please excuse me.

596
00:28:16,510 --> 00:28:18,596
Music unit, let's go.

597
00:28:19,420 --> 00:28:20,012
Cheers.

598
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:21,030
Cheers.

599
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:33,378
♪ Don't be afraid even
if we are separated ♪

600
00:28:33,390 --> 00:28:38,572
♪ Just stay there and wait for me,
I'll find you ♪

601
00:28:38,621 --> 00:28:41,870
♪ No matter what tomorrow brings ♪

602
00:28:41,889 --> 00:28:44,676
♪ Please remember this ♪

603
00:28:44,701 --> 00:28:48,363
♪ I will live ♪

604
00:28:49,790 --> 00:28:52,953
♪ Only for you ♪

605
00:28:56,280 --> 00:29:01,501
This song is for
faithful couples like you two.

606
00:29:02,330 --> 00:29:03,033
Thank you.

607
00:29:03,064 --> 00:29:04,064
Thank you.

608
00:29:06,170 --> 00:29:08,646
He came on his own.

609
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:16,498
Food unit, let's go!

610
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:43,790
The food's here.

611
00:29:49,027 --> 00:29:50,027
Here you go.

612
00:29:51,010 --> 00:29:51,975
Thank you.

613
00:29:52,006 --> 00:29:53,569
Enjoy your meal.

614
00:29:53,581 --> 00:29:54,581
Congratulations.

615
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,701
Oh? What's the occasion?

616
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:59,790
You two looked so sweet together.

617
00:29:59,815 --> 00:30:01,347
I thought you were getting engaged.

618
00:30:01,378 --> 00:30:02,378
Am I right?

619
00:30:03,290 --> 00:30:04,290
We just started dating.

620
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:06,289
Really? Oh.

621
00:30:06,313 --> 00:30:10,110
But it probably won't be long.

622
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,470
Congratulations.

623
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:17,138
Enjoy your meal.

624
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:19,790
Come on.

625
00:30:19,890 --> 00:30:20,890
Let's eat.

626
00:30:32,820 --> 00:30:33,820
How is it?

627
00:30:35,610 --> 00:30:36,670
So good.

628
00:30:36,689 --> 00:30:37,963
Mm.

629
00:30:49,890 --> 00:30:50,455
Uh…

630
00:30:50,730 --> 00:30:54,400
Excuse me. I need to go to the bathroom.

631
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:56,713
Are you okay, Veha?

632
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:59,729
I've got a weird stomachache.

633
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:01,120
Excuse me.

634
00:31:26,750 --> 00:31:29,483
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
I MISS YOU SO MUCH, KANIT.

635
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:32,196
How dare he text me this?

636
00:31:38,540 --> 00:31:41,156
MISS ME? WANT ME TO COME OVER?

637
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:50,566
Time to reclaim your dignity,

638
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:52,793
Nopnapha.

639
00:31:54,732 --> 00:31:58,467
Kanit will no longer be your victim.

640
00:32:07,570 --> 00:32:08,836
How are you feeling, Veha?

641
00:32:08,855 --> 00:32:09,855
Are you okay?

642
00:32:11,390 --> 00:32:14,744
You miss me, so here I am.

643
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:16,781
Am I a good boyfriend?

644
00:32:20,744 --> 00:32:22,080
What brings you here?

645
00:32:24,220 --> 00:32:25,975
Familiar vibes, huh?

646
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:27,384
You really care about the planet.

647
00:32:28,050 --> 00:32:31,070
You keep recycling your tricks.

648
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,553
It's not what you think.

649
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:38,209
It's not what I think.

650
00:32:38,227 --> 00:32:39,538
I saw it with my own eyes.

651
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:46,000
Why? Am I not enough for you?

652
00:32:47,750 --> 00:32:49,403
It's not like that.

653
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:53,809
He and I are just talking casually.

654
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:55,852
Talking casually?

655
00:32:55,876 --> 00:32:57,932
If you want to talk, you can talk to me.

656
00:32:57,950 --> 00:32:58,950
I'm good at talking.

657
00:33:02,020 --> 00:33:05,624
Stop making excuses
and just admit you're a jerk.

658
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,950
I know I'm a jerk,

659
00:33:13,970 --> 00:33:15,821
but I…

660
00:33:17,530 --> 00:33:18,806
just want some excitement.

661
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:20,923
Excitement? If that's what you want,

662
00:33:20,947 --> 00:33:23,009
there are plenty of things you can do.

663
00:33:23,027 --> 00:33:24,332
Go swim with sharks.

664
00:33:24,375 --> 00:33:25,353
Base jump off a building.

665
00:33:25,384 --> 00:33:26,584
Jump out of a helicopter.

666
00:33:26,609 --> 00:33:28,356
Or jump anywhere you want.

667
00:33:28,381 --> 00:33:29,969
But not cheating!

668
00:33:35,150 --> 00:33:37,280
Allow me to change the photos
to match the mood.

669
00:33:43,120 --> 00:33:44,615
Leave writing novels

670
00:33:45,580 --> 00:33:48,289
to high school students on their break.

671
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:52,600
Stop making up stories already.

672
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:02,449
♪ Why would I regret losing a crappy guy ♪

673
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:05,686
♪ Like you? Just why? ♪

674
00:34:05,716 --> 00:34:12,092
♪ Who knows where dating you
would take my life? ♪

675
00:34:12,123 --> 00:34:15,230
♪ A playboy day and night ♪

676
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:18,270
♪ Cheating when the chance arises ♪

677
00:34:18,289 --> 00:34:21,489
♪ I'm totally fine ♪

678
00:34:21,501 --> 00:34:24,572
♪ Just losing a crappy guy ♪

679
00:34:24,609 --> 00:34:27,716
♪ Like you ♪

680
00:34:28,990 --> 00:34:30,732
That's a song for a nice vibe.

681
00:34:38,730 --> 00:34:39,810
What's the meaning of this?

682
00:34:44,410 --> 00:34:45,224
Veha,

683
00:34:45,243 --> 00:34:46,243
hear me out.

684
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:50,400
Veha!

685
00:34:54,690 --> 00:35:01,360
♪ Why would I regret losing a crappy guy
like you? Just why? ♪

686
00:35:01,396 --> 00:35:07,396
♪ Who knows where dating you
would take my life? ♪

687
00:35:07,427 --> 00:35:10,393
♪ A playboy day and night ♪

688
00:35:10,430 --> 00:35:13,353
♪ Cheating when the chance arises ♪

689
00:35:13,384 --> 00:35:16,258
♪ I'm totally fine ♪

690
00:35:16,307 --> 00:35:24,227
♪ Just losing a crappy guy like you ♪

691
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:42,660
Veha.

692
00:35:43,470 --> 00:35:44,470
Veha.

693
00:35:46,750 --> 00:35:47,750
Can I talk to you?

694
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,963
Can I talk to you, please?

695
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,593
You said you were breaking up with him.

696
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:52,929
What was that?

697
00:35:53,698 --> 00:35:55,690
How am I going to show my face
after what he did?

698
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:58,603
I was really going to break up with him.

699
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:01,095
And I'm so angry

700
00:36:02,147 --> 00:36:04,147
that he was completely disrespectful
to both of us.

701
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:07,409
I'm going to deal with the people
who humiliated you.

702
00:36:07,690 --> 00:36:09,330
How are you going to take responsibility?

703
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:13,218
I'm going to talk it out with him.

704
00:36:14,270 --> 00:36:14,996
Talk?

705
00:36:15,220 --> 00:36:16,916
You've said that dozens of times already.

706
00:36:17,830 --> 00:36:19,750
I feel like I've been
getting lied to every day.

707
00:36:19,980 --> 00:36:20,996
Veha,

708
00:36:21,015 --> 00:36:22,670
please calm down.

709
00:36:22,707 --> 00:36:23,707
Calm down?

710
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,110
I've stayed calm for a year already.

711
00:36:27,860 --> 00:36:29,107
I've been so stupid.

712
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:31,033
Veha…

713
00:36:32,490 --> 00:36:33,483
I'm sorry.

714
00:36:33,507 --> 00:36:34,507
Don't touch me!

715
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:36,381
I really didn't mean it.

716
00:36:37,030 --> 00:36:40,941
This time, I'm really choosing you.

717
00:36:42,040 --> 00:36:45,101
You're only choosing me
because no one else wants you anymore.

718
00:36:46,780 --> 00:36:47,780
Veha,

719
00:36:50,590 --> 00:36:54,123
can we not be like this?

720
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:58,110
Veha, please.

721
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:00,190
Don't leave me too.

722
00:37:04,790 --> 00:37:06,215
Don't do this to anyone again.

723
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,689
Veha.

724
00:37:38,410 --> 00:37:39,410
I don't want to say this,

725
00:37:40,670 --> 00:37:41,673
but I warned you.

726
00:37:44,890 --> 00:37:46,615
If you're here to gloat,

727
00:37:47,593 --> 00:37:48,610
just say it.

728
00:37:50,610 --> 00:37:53,341
If you're going to insult me, just do it.

729
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:55,716
I'm an asshole.

730
00:37:57,083 --> 00:37:58,178
I'm terrible.

731
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:02,184
I deserve what's happening to me.

732
00:38:05,330 --> 00:38:06,330
Go ahead and insult me.

733
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,289
I'm waiting to hear it.

734
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,209
Insult me.

735
00:38:11,640 --> 00:38:12,763
Do it.

736
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,393
Insult me.

737
00:38:14,720 --> 00:38:16,006
Go ahead and insult me!

738
00:38:16,024 --> 00:38:17,255
Just do it!

739
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:27,820
I won't.

740
00:38:29,563 --> 00:38:31,844
I just want you to know
you're not anyone's second choice.

741
00:38:45,810 --> 00:38:49,821
I feel so worthless.

742
00:38:50,720 --> 00:38:51,963
Just own up to your mistake.

743
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:55,064
You can start over.

744
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:58,104
If I weren't in the picture,

745
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:01,470
everyone would be happier, wouldn't they?

746
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:21,569
Did you see his face when you showed up?

747
00:39:21,770 --> 00:39:23,661
I was so damn satisfied.

748
00:39:23,698 --> 00:39:25,058
He looked so shocked.

749
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:28,806
I should've taken a photo
and posted it on social media.

750
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:30,338
It would've gone viral for sure.

751
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:35,190
Hey.

752
00:39:35,770 --> 00:39:36,787
Aren't you satisfied?

753
00:39:41,610 --> 00:39:42,610
Hey.

754
00:39:43,370 --> 00:39:44,370
Hey.

755
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,150
Are you okay?

756
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:47,630
Hey.

757
00:39:50,050 --> 00:39:51,050
Hey.

758
00:39:52,150 --> 00:39:52,615
Hey!

759
00:39:52,910 --> 00:39:53,698
Hey!

760
00:39:53,723 --> 00:39:54,387
What are you doing?

761
00:39:54,412 --> 00:39:55,412
Hey!

762
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,000
Hey!

763
00:39:58,220 --> 00:39:59,335
Calm down.

764
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:00,560
Please listen to me.

765
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,633
It's just a bad guy.

766
00:40:03,220 --> 00:40:04,620
Don't throw your life away for him.

767
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:08,972
You'll find someone good. Trust me.

768
00:40:11,100 --> 00:40:12,843
You have so many people who love you.

769
00:40:13,809 --> 00:40:15,209
Please don't jump. I'm begging you.

770
00:40:15,980 --> 00:40:16,980
Hey!

771
00:40:22,270 --> 00:40:23,270
Hey.

772
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:25,132
I wasn't going to jump.

773
00:40:25,310 --> 00:40:26,310
I just came to throw up.

774
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:28,190
Oh.

775
00:40:29,950 --> 00:40:30,978
Get it out.

776
00:40:31,670 --> 00:40:32,670
Want some water?

777
00:40:42,410 --> 00:40:43,410
Here.

778
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:44,603
Drink up.

779
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:46,960
Thank you.

780
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:59,544
The way you ran, I thought
you were going to jump off the building.

781
00:41:00,530 --> 00:41:01,530
You startled me.

782
00:41:02,330 --> 00:41:03,956
I wouldn't do anything like that.

783
00:41:04,790 --> 00:41:05,975
It was just too much.

784
00:41:06,410 --> 00:41:07,618
My heart was racing.

785
00:41:07,636 --> 00:41:09,126
And my stomach was all upset.

786
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:11,796
I couldn't take it. I
had to get it all out.

787
00:41:12,640 --> 00:41:13,880
I get it. I know it's not easy.

788
00:41:14,490 --> 00:41:15,575
But you did great.

789
00:41:17,740 --> 00:41:19,003
You got it over with.

790
00:41:22,658 --> 00:41:25,987
Now you don't have to
obsess over it anymore.

791
00:41:29,630 --> 00:41:33,587
I've wasted so many years
on a pipe dream.

792
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,160
It's just like when you warned me

793
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:42,000
about dropping dead.

794
00:41:45,080 --> 00:41:47,384
I was just rambling.

795
00:41:48,060 --> 00:41:49,409
I didn't mean it like that.

796
00:41:55,290 --> 00:41:57,384
If Lion can't make your dream come true,

797
00:41:58,770 --> 00:42:00,410
why don't you find someone else to do it?

798
00:42:14,590 --> 00:42:16,929
I'm both relieved and sad.

799
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:20,824
I'm relieved it's over,

800
00:42:23,409 --> 00:42:25,400
but I'm sad I used to love
a bad guy like him.

801
00:42:29,040 --> 00:42:30,486
Take it as a life lesson.

802
00:42:32,130 --> 00:42:33,458
You did your best.

803
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,190
Cut that shitty person out of your life.

804
00:42:36,990 --> 00:42:38,812
None of it was your fault.

805
00:42:39,890 --> 00:42:41,304
You were a good boyfriend.

806
00:42:42,570 --> 00:42:44,406
If he doesn't see your worth,

807
00:42:51,300 --> 00:42:52,775
you have to see it yourself.

808
00:43:00,770 --> 00:43:02,184
Can you not touch me?

809
00:43:03,630 --> 00:43:05,452
If someone were kind to me right now,

810
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:07,833
I'd definitely cry.

811
00:43:08,810 --> 00:43:10,381
Then I won't let go of your hand.

812
00:43:11,850 --> 00:43:13,600
Whatever's on your mind, let it all out.

813
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:15,920
I'll take it.

814
00:43:51,101 --> 00:43:52,101
Cry it out.

815
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:53,680
Cry it all out.

816
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:08,818
(Next Episode)
Stop crying and open the door for me.

817
00:44:08,830 --> 00:44:10,806
If you're here to rub it in,

818
00:44:10,830 --> 00:44:11,830
then just leave.

819
00:44:12,460 --> 00:44:14,100
Here are tools for letting out your rage.

820
00:44:16,270 --> 00:44:17,270
Thank you

821
00:44:17,500 --> 00:44:19,076
for making today not so bad.

822
00:44:19,883 --> 00:44:22,123
Who would be into someone for that long?

823
00:44:22,153 --> 00:44:24,480
Are you sure you're not into me anymore?

824
00:44:26,480 --> 00:44:27,680
Can you sleep with me tonight?

825
00:44:28,160 --> 00:44:29,169
You mean

826
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:31,243
sleeping next to each other?

